  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we figured it out that there was like little window opening on the attic, so we figured it out that this will be the third-- third joint where we will look for it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we told all my sisters and we told my parents that where is the jewelry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But the meantime, we didn't think about taking out the earrings from our ears, because it was so natural that-- so when the gendarmes had seen that we have the earrings and the-- so he said, I want you to give me all your jewelry, all your money, all the valuables, if you have any certificate, bonds, and this and that.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And after the war, you will-- you will reimbursed for it or you will get it back, and they will give you a receipt for it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we took all the jewelry, everything, and we put it on the table.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one of my youngest-- my sister Eva, she was with my grandparents in another town for the second part of the holiday of-- of Passover.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we told him that we are-- we are missing one sister of mine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He made a note of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after that, he said, you know, Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Czigler, I like you very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I like your family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, I would suggest that you take food with you, whatever you can, because you don't know how long you will be there and where you will be.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, he said, take you-- because the Jewish people was rendering the goose fat, and we had like different size of dishes that we were storing it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, he said, if you have flour or if you have beans or whatever you have, take it with you.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
